<B=15>TypeScript 1.1
& TypeScript 1.1 &
 _____                 ____            _       _     _   _ 
|_   _|   _ _ __   ___/ ___|  ___ _ __(_)_ __ | |_  / | / |
  | || | | | '_ \ / _ \___ \ / __| '__| | '_ \| __| | | | |
  | || |_| | |_) |  __/___) | (__| |  | | |_) | |_  | |_| |
